    [data] glyph.ha  8×16 bitmap font (scaffolding, dissolves with SDF)
    walks/
      input.asm        keyboard + mouse poll walk (producer)
      mouse.asm        cursor drawing scaffolding (dissolves into walk)
      speaker.asm      440Hz beep walk
